apk update

Install stress-ng:

apk add stress-ng

Verify installation:

    stress-ng --version

    You should see the installed version of stress-ng.

Using stress-ng in Alpine

stress-ng offers similar functionality to stress with additional features:

    Generate CPU load:

stress-ng --cpu 4 --timeout 30s

    Utilizes 4 CPU cores.
    Runs for 30 seconds.

Generate memory load:

stress-ng --vm 1 --vm-bytes 300M --timeout 30s

    Allocates memory on 2 virtual memory workers.
    Each worker allocates 256 MB.
    Runs for 30 seconds.

Simulate both CPU and memory load:

stress-ng --cpu 2 --vm 1 --vm-bytes 512M --timeout 30s

